Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:36.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All of you, get off the island! - OG}Todos vocês precisam sair dessa ilha!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:41.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que quer dizer, Sentomaru{-san}?!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:45.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What is happening on the island?! - OG}O que tá acontecendo nessa ilha?!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:49.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que você ativou os pacifista\Npor toda a ilha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:58.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Há muito tempo, uma ilha chamada Ohara\Ndesapareceu de repente do mapa mundial.
Comment: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:57.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, an island called Ohara suddenly disappeared from the world map.
Comment: 0,0:01:57.72,0:01:58.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, an island called Ohara suddenly disappeared from the world map.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:05.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Because they rebelled against\Nthe World Government. - OG}Tudo porque desafiaram o Governo Mundial.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:10.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Incidente de Ohara...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:17.12,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{It took place on the island of Ohara,\Nhome to the world's largest historical library. - OG}Na ilha de Ohara, lar da\Nmaior biblioteca histórica do mundo...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:23.46,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Scholars and residents who attempted\Nto decipher the poneglyphs... - OG}estudiosos trabalhavam pra decifrar os poneglyphs,\Num ato proibido pelo governo.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:25.50,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{which was forbidden by the government... - OG}Em consequência, os moradores da ilha...{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:30.96,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{were killed in a Marine bombardment. - OG}foram exterminados num bombardeio da Marinha.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:34.84,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Only a single girl survived. - OG}A única sobrevivente daquele incidente...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:37.76,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Nico Robin. - OG}foi Nico Robin.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:46.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The fact that Old Man Punk, who has\Nthe best brain in the world, is being targeted... - OG}Se estão tentando matar o Velho Punk,\No homem mais inteligente do mundo...{Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:49.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{means they contemplated all the losses... - OG}significa que eles consideraram o custo...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:54.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but still decided that he should be killed. - OG}e ainda assim decidiram que a cabeça dele vale o preço.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:02.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If so, a worse incident\Nthan the one at Ohara... - OG}Se isso é verdade, então algo\Nainda pior que Ohara...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:06.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{could happen here soon! - OG}pode acontecer nessa ilha!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,60)}{Hurry up, Straw Hat! - OG}Rápido, Chapéu de Palha!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:22.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What's happening up there now?! - OG}Que diabos tá acontecendo lá em cima...?!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Hand Pistol...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}...Yellow Lotus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:09.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}...Kong Organ!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Tempest Kick...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:30.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Tumult!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}White Thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:39.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}One-Sword Style Draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:49.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Lethal Lion Song!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:23.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:25.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's enough, you guys! - OG}Chega, seus malditos!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:33.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're getting up too many times! - OG}Parem de levantar de uma vez!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:34.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês são o Kaido por acaso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:37.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que nossos ataques não funcionam neles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:38.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é mesmo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:44.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They remind me of King who I fought in Wano. - OG}Eles me lembram aquele\NKing que eu lutei em Wano.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:48.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There was a lunarian in Kaido's pirate group?! - OG}Tinha um lunariano na tripulação do Kaido?{WF/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:51.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't know the name of his tribe but... - OG}Não peguei o nome da raça dele...{WF+Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:53.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendo...
Comment: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:56.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That man is probably the guinea pig... - OG}{Some time ago, Kaido escaped Punk Hazard... - PJ+Polly}Kaido escaped Punk Hazard a long time ago,{Polly}
Comment: 0,0:05:56.38,0:06:01.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{who escaped from Punk Hazard\Nwith Kaido a long time ago... Alber. - OG}along with a test subject named Alber.\NThat is likely the same man.{PJ+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:06:00.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That man is probably the guinea pig who escaped from Punk Hazard with Kaido a long time ago... - OG}{\q2}Aquele homem provavelmente é a cobaia que\Nescapou de Punk Hazard com o Kaido tempos atrás...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:01.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Alber. - OG}chamado Alber.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:04.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The seraphim were indeed... - OG}Os Seraphim foram mesmo...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:08.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,aprimorados com o sangue lunariano dele.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:10.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh yeah?! - OG}Então é assim, é...?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:14.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then watch the flames\Non their backs carefully, guys! - OG}Nesse caso, fiquem de olho\Nnas chamas deles, pessoal!{Polly+Camo+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:19.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Your attack only works\Non them when the flames are out. - OG}Nossos ataques só funcionam quando elas apagam.{Polly+Camo+WF}
Comment: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:20.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:22.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{When it's burning, they're almost invincible. - OG}Quando o fogo tá aceso, eles são praticamente invencíveis.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:28.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry I wasted your energy! - OG}Desculpa, acho que desperdicei muita energia.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:31.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I should've noticed it sooner. - OG}Eu devia ter percebido antes.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:35.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, it's just in time.\NNow we know how to fight them. - OG}Antes tarde do que nunca.\NAgora sabemos como lutar contra eles.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:37.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{King's characteristics are... - OG}As características marcantes do King eram...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:38.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,cabelo branco...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:40.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,pele escura...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:42.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,asas negras...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:45.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e as chamas nas costas.
