Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:50.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Você devia ter percebido antes!\N– Você devia ter percebido antes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:56.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Aonde você vai, Capacete?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:01.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I have an idea of one place\Nwhere Stella might be. - OG}Acho que sei onde a Stella pode estar.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:08.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:11.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sorry to give you trouble. - OG}Desculpa pelo incômodo.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't get in our way! - OG}Não se mete!{Polly (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're in a hurry. - OG}A gente tá com pressa!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:27.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Zeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:30.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele não é uma criança!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:34.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tá machucando meus amigos!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He half-destroyed Edison! - OG}Ele quase destruiu o Edison!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:38.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele é uma máquina de matar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:42.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele não é fofo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele não é uma criança!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:45.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:47.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não hesita!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Close your eyes if you want! - OG}Fecha os olhos se precisar!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:50.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Push me out! - OG}Só me coloca lá!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Leave the rest to me! - OG}Eu cuido do resto!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Thunderbolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não foi suficiente!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I won't let you get away! - OG}Te peguei!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:14.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I got you! - OG}Na mosca!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:20.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sorry! Jinbe. - OG}Me desculpa, Jinbe...{Polly/WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele mergulhou de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:27.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Corre!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:32.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Nami-san, he's coming from the bottom! - OG}Nami, ele vai atacar por baixo!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:33.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não funcionou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:52.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Constitution of Sanji Kingdom, Article 1. - OG}Artigo 1 da Sanjistituição:{Polly (Viz)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:55.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Those who scare Nami-san will face... - OG}A punição por assustar a Nami...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:56.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{the death penalty! - OG}é a morte!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Aubad–{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:06.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Constitution of Sanji Kingdom, Article 9. - OG}Artigo 9 da Sanjistituição:{Polly (Viz)}
Comment: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,The Constitution of Sanji Kingdom,
Comment: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Article 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:10.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Those who make Nami-san scream will face... - OG}A punição por fazer a Nami gritar é...{Polly+Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Raw Heat Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji{-kun}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:28.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Nami - -san}{, are you hurt? - OG}Nami, ele te machucou?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:29.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you okay? - OG}Você tá bem?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:30.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Thank you! - OG}Tô bem, obrigada!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm glad that you're fine. - OG}Que bom.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:34.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll take care of him now. - OG}Agora vou acabar com ele.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:38.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I warned you! You shitty brat! - OG}Eu avisei, seu pirralho de merda!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:46.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whether you're a brat or Jinbe... - OG}Não importa se é criança\Nou se é o próprio Jinbe...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:49.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna execute you! - OG}a pena é de morte do mesmo jeito.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:51.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Little Jinbe! - OG}Jinbe Júnior!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:57.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How dare you turn York into stone! - OG}Como ousa petrificar a York?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:09:59.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What can we do?! - OG}O que a gente faz?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:04.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Enjoy the taste of the bubble gun! - OG}Toma um gostinho da arma de bolhas!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's not working at all! - OG}Não funcionou nada!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:18.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:21.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You lowered your guard! - OG}Vacilou!{Polly}
Comment: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:23.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:29.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The bubbles that are created\Nin this gun are filled with sea energy. - OG}As bolhas que essa engenhoca cria\Nsão carregadas com a energia do mar!{Z/Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:34.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{And green blood has the same\Nweakness as power-users! - OG}E esse sangue verde dá a mesma\Nfraqueza dos usuários de poder!{Polly/PJ/WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:37.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So the bubble weakens you. - OG}Ou seja, as bolhas te enfraquecem!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's amazing, Lilith! - OG}Isso é demais, Lilith!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:43.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, isn't it?! - OG}Pode apostar!{LP+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All right! - OG}Isso aí!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:47.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's our chance to restrain her! - OG}Agora é nossa chance de prender ela!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:49.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixa comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:58.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't touch me! - OG}Me solte!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:03.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You insolent fellow! - OG}Seu insolente!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:05.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Behave yourself! - OG}Conheça o seu lugar!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:07.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's already worn off! - OG}O efeito já passou!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:09.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It only grazed her arm. - OG}É porque só raspou no braço dela.{Polly/WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pelo menos devia ter grudado nela!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:13.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Come on! Gee! - OG}Seus malvados! Idiotas!{Polly+LP+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:15.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Come on! Come on! - OG}Bobões!{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She's pissed! - OG}Ela tá fazendo birra!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:24.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She's gonna shoot a laser! Retreat for now! - OG}É um laser! Melhor correr!{Polly/WF/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:26.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-S-Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:28.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Corre!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:32.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{S-Snake! Don't do it! - OG}S-Snake! Pare!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're just a seraphim! Don't be rude! - OG}Você é só um Seraphim! Não seja pirralha!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:51.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Baixou a guarda!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:59.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How's that? You damn brat! - OG}Gostou dessa, pirralha?!{Polly+LP+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:04.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're so smart, Franky! - OG}Boa ideia, Franky!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:07.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Bubble guns are useful! - OG}Armas de bolha são bem úteis!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:12.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Give up, you brat! - OG}Desiste, sua pestinha!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:17.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm... in pain... - OG}Você... tá me machucando...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:23.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Perfume Femur!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:27.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No! I'm getting petrified! - OG}Droga! Tô virando pedra!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn! - OG}Droga!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:33.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Franky is petrified! - OG}O Franky foi petrificado!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's not good! - OG}Isso é ruim!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:36.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele vai morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:41.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She's coming this way! - OG}Ela tá vindo!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:03.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Love-Love Mellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:10.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Lilith!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:28.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O único lugar onde a Stella poderia estar...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:31.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,é nessa sala...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:32.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem é você?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:37.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Foi você que fez isso com a gente?{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:39.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't tell me... - OG}Não me diz que...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{you're the Cipher Pol agents\Nwho came to the island a while ago! - OG}Vocês são os agentes da Cipher Pol de antes!{Polly}
Comment: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:41.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... you're the Cipher Pol agents who came to the island a while ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:42.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que vocês estão aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nos ajudem...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:46.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tirem a gente daqui...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:50.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não quero morrer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:56.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Stella!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:03.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're here! - OG}Então era aqui que você estava!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem fez isso com você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:09.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Shaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:15.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm glad that you're okay! - OG}Que bom que você tá bem!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll unlock the door now! - OG}Vou destrancar a porta!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:17.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Shaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:22.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who are you here with? - OG}Quem tá com você?{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:22.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Shaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:42.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He got shot! - OG}Ele levou um tiro!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why?! - OG}Mas por quê?!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:13.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Keep your guard up. - OG}Fiquem alertas.{Polly/WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:14.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sim, senhor!\N– Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:27.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O quê?! Tio Kizaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:28.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:33.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele está vindo pra cá com uma frota\Nde mais de cem embarcações de todos os tamanhos.{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:36.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mais de cem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:41.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{CP0's mission is to kill Doctor\Nand wait for Kizaru's arrival. - OG}A missão da CP0 é eliminar\No doutor e esperar o Kizaru chegar.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're sending a Marine admiral... - OG}Então vão mandar um almirante da Marinha...{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:47.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The government's stance\Nis out of the ordinary... - OG}Eles estão levando isso muito a sério...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:48.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yes. - OG}De fato.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:51.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{They must be taking the situation\Nmore seriously than they did with Ohara. - OG}Devem considerar isso ainda pior que Ohara.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:52.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:53.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Razão um:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:57.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Doctor has inherited\NOhara's forbidden research, - OG}O doutor está continuando\Na pesquisa proibida de Ohara.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:16:00.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{and is making progress with it. - OG}Mais que isso, ele está fazendo muito progresso.{Polly+Camo+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:02.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Reason two. - OG}E razão dois:{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:07.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Egghead has battle capabilities\Nwhich Ohara didn't have! - OG}Diferente de Ohara, Egghead\Ntem capacidade de revidar.{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:09.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You mean the seraphim\Nand all of the pacifista? - OG}Você quer dizer os Seraphim e\No exército de pacifista?{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:15.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, those are good enough reasons\Nfor enormous forces to be deployed. - OG}Quando você coloca assim,\Num ataque em peso faz sentido.{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:18.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Contact me when anything happens! - OG}Me avise se acontecer alguma coisa!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{All communication devices\Nin the Labophase are inoperative. - OG}Os sistemas de comunicação\Nda Labophase estão todos fora do ar.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:22.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Did you hear that?! - OG}Ouviram tudo isso?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:32.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Learn from history what\Nthe Marines are gonna do here! - OG}A história nos diz tudo que precisamos saber\Nsobre o que a Marinha vai fazer aqui!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:36.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are we, and this research facility,\Ngoing to suffer the same fate as Ohara?! - OG}Está dizendo que tanto nós quanto\Nessas instalações vão ter o mesmo fim de Ohara?!{LP+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:37.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right! - OG}Exatamente!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's no time to think! - OG}Vocês não podem hesitar agora!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:42.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hurry up and get off of Egghead! - OG}Rápido e evacuem Egghead!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:43.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vão!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get the ship ready! - OG}Preparem os navios!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:48.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We'll leave the island! - OG}Temos que sair da ilha!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Antes que a Marinha chegue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:52.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just as Sentomaru-san told us! - OG}Ouçam o Sentomaru!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:55.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Lilith!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You shitty brat! - OG}Sua pirralha!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:16:59.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Unpetrify me! - OG}Me volta ao normal!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:03.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I lowered my guard on my right side, - OG}Vacilei do lado direito...{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:06.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but I still got my left side! - OG}mas meu esquerdo tá inteiro!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:10.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quer experimentar meu Weapons Left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:14.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But if you surrender now, maybe I'll forgive... - OG}Se desistir agora, {\i1}talvez{\i0} eu te perdoe...{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:19.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No... I just... - OG}Hm, eu só tava...{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, are you listening?! - OG}Ei, volta aqui!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:27.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll shoot you if you don't stop! - OG}Para ou eu atiro!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:30.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why?! S-Snake! - OG}Por quê, S-Snake?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:34.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Whose... Whose orders\Nare you working under?! - OG}Quem... Quem tá mandando você fazer tudo isso?!{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Please don't do it! - OG}Por favor, espere!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:40.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:43.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pythagoras!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera! Ei!{OG}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wait! - OG}Espera, droga!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:04.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wonder if everyone's okay... - OG}Espero que estejam todos bem...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:08.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've been hearing\Nhuge explosions and screams. - OG}Não paro de ouvir um monte de gritos e explosões.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:11.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We know that the seraphim are rampaging. - OG}Bom, sabemos que os Seraphim estão descontrolados.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:14.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's incomprehensible! - OG}Não consigo entender!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu achava que os Seraphim estavam do nosso lado...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:21.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Perhaps someone overrode\Nthe command again. - OG}Talvez alguém tenha sobrescrito\Nas ordens deles de novo.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:25.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tô preocupada com a Nami e os outros...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:27.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles vão ficar bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:30.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's a person who instantly rushes\Nto her when he hears her scream. - OG}Se a Nami gritar, tem uma certa pessoa\Nque corre pro lado dela na hora.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:31.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, you're right! - OG}Ah, é verdade!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:39.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Teams in combat can't go anywhere. - OG}Quem tá lutando não pode sair do lugar.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:44.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{While everyone's fighting, there's the risk\Nof something happening to Vegapunk. - OG}Algo pode acontecer\Ncom o Vegapunk enquanto isso.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:46.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! Let's find him ASAP! - OG}Boa! Vamos logo encontrá-lo!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:51.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, there is a room that was once\Nused and is now sealed off. - OG}Pensando bem, tem aquele\Nlaboratório antigo que selamos...{Polly+Camo+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:52.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{– What?!\N– What?! - OG}– O quê?\N– O quê?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:56.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't think anyone would go there though... - OG}Não sei por que alguém\Niria lá, mas...{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:57.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos verificar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:19:01.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Maybe we'll find some trace of a clue. - OG}Talvez a gente encontre alguma pista, pelo menos.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Show us the way, Atlas! - OG}Mostra o caminho, Atlas!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:04.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! - OG}Pode deixar!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:16.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Edison, fica comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:19.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Edison!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:24.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Nami-san! I'll lighten myself up\Nand go find Vegapunk! - OG}Nami! Vou perder uns quilos\Ne ir procurar o Vegapunk!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:25.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Uh-huh! - OG}Tá!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:33.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:50.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sanji-san! You're awesome! - OG}Sanji, você é incrível!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:56.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Little Jinbe... - OG}Jinbe Júnior...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:58.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you know... - OG}Será que você sabe...{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:20:00.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{the power of love?! - OG}o poder do amor?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:06.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:09.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Red Hawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:19.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn! The flames on their backs\Nhaven't gone out yet! - OG}Droga! As chamas nas costas\Ndeles não se apagam!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:26.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! While we were focused on their flames,\Nthe Hawk Eye look-alike is gone! - OG}Ei! O cara que parece com o Olho de Falcão sumiu!{Polly+LP+Z+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Where did he go?! - OG}Pra onde ele foi?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:30.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They must've changed their target priority. - OG}Ele deve ter mudado a prioridade dos alvos.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:34.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They'll save the troublesome ones\Nfor later and eliminate the weak ones first. - OG}Ele tá deixando os difíceis pro final\Ne indo atrás dos mais fracos.{Polly+Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:41.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That way, they could also upset\Nthe tough ones by killing their friends. - OG}Ver os amigos morrerem também desmoraliza\Nos oponentes mais fortes.{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy, leave him to me! - OG}Luffy, deixa comigo!{Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:44.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll chase him! - OG}Eu vou atrás dele!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:45.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tô contando com você, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:46.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh no! - OG}Ah, droga!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:48.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Usopp!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:49.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai com ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:52.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He can get lost easily! - OG}Ele vai se perder!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:54.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's so high-maintenance! - OG}Vocês tão me matando de trabalhar!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:57.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wait, Roronoa! - OG}Calma aí, Roronoa!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:59.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, did you call me "Usopp"?! - OG}Ei, quem você tá chamando de "Usopp"?!{Polly+Camo}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tá lutando comigo{\i1} agora{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.09,0:21:19.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:22.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Hawk Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:24.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Apaga, fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:26.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You fool. Wait, Straw Hat! - OG}Idiota! Para, Chapéu de Palha!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:27.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Think! - OG}Usa a cabeça!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:30.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Assim você nunca vai vencer ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:41.70,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is everything that happened the day\Nbefore the famous Egghead Incident. - OG}{\q2}Essa foi toda a história do que aconteceu\Nna véspera do infame Incidente de Egghead...{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:46.62,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{But it all started three months earlier. - OG}Porém, a história realmente começa\Ntrês meses antes...{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.58,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(683,27)}A Terra Sagrada, Mary Geoise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:54.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...é...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:55.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...g... ...d...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:59.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aqui é E... ...d...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.30,0:22:00.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não consigo ouvir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:04.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aqui é Egghe... ...d...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.64,0:22:06.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Preciso falar com... ...uperiores.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:08.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What do you want from them?! - OG}Qual é o seu assunto?{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:10.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...preciso falar com os superiores...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:12.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I said "What do you want?!" - OG}Eu disse declare o seu assunto!{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.69,0:22:15.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O Dr. Vegapunk está...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:18.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}pesquisando o Século Perdido.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.62,0:22:39.00,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Upon receiving that tip, CP5 was dispatched\Nto Egghead to verify the truth, - OG}Após receber essa informação, a CP5 foi enviada\Na Egghead para verificar a veracidade...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:41.84,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{but found no evidence. - OG}mas voltou de mãos vazias.{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.26,0:22:44.84,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{After completing the investigation, - OG}Com a investigação concluída,\Neles partiram...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:47.97,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{the ship mysteriously\Ndisappeared on its way back. - OG}só pra o navio desaparecer sem deixar rastro.{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.19,0:22:57.40,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Para investigar o desaparecimento,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:23:03.11,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{first CP7, then CP8 headed to Egghead, - OG}mais agentes da CP7, depois da CP8,\Nforam enviados a Egghead...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:06.82,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{but no one returned to the government. - OG}mas nenhum retornou ao governo.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:10.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aqui é Egghead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:13.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Me passem pros superiores.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.05,0:23:28.39,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Later, there was a meeting between\Nthe Five Elders and another figure, - OG}Após uma reunião entre os Cinco Anciãos\Ne essa figura misteriosa...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:32.47,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{and the betrayal of the genius scientist\Nresearching the Void Century... - OG}a traição do cientista gênio\Nque pesquisava o Século Perdido...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:34.68,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{became clear. - OG}ficou absolutamente clara.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.77,0:23:40.98,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Five Elders decided\Non Dr. Vegapunk's assassination. - OG}Os Cinco Anciãos decidiram que Vegapunk\Nseria assassinado.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.74,0:23:48.28,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{Cipher Pol "Aigis" 0,\Ntasked with that mission, set sail. - OG}A Cipher Pol Aigis 0 foi encarregada\Nde executar a missão e partiu.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:53.62,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{However, one of the Five Elders\Ndecided to go in person, - OG}Porém, os Cinco Anciãos esperavam\Nresistência de Vegapunk,{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.62,0:23:56.04,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{in anticipation of Vegapunk's counterattack. - OG}e decidiram supervisionar pessoalmente.{WF+Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.04,0:24:00.17,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{He assigned Admiral Kizaru as his escort. - OG}O Almirante Kizaru foi escolhido como escolta.{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:11.60,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{In addition, reinforcements were requested\Nto various Marine branches. - OG}Além disso, um pedido de reforços\Nfoi enviado a várias bases da Marinha.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.85,0:24:20.61,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{The deployment was on the scale of a war. - OG}A mobilização era como se\Nestivessem se preparando pra guerra.{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.54,0:24:38.50,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{However, another ship came calling... - OG}Porém, um visitante inesperado apareceu...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.50,0:24:43.46,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{That of the Emperor of the Sea,\NStraw Hat Luffy. - OG}o navio do Imperador Chapéu de Palha Luffy.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.81,0:25:00.85,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{The government was not content\Nwith the unexpected intruders' landing. - OG}O governo se incomodou\Ncom a chegada imprevista dos intrusos.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.85,0:25:02.11,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá vendo?!{EH08 03:36}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.86,0:25:06.19,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,As coisas tão se complicando de novo!{EH08 03:38}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.91,0:25:12.57,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's them again! - OG}Eles de novo?!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.45,0:25:16.08,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{In any case... - OG}De qualquer forma...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.08,0:25:18.91,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{the incident will come to an end the next day, - OG}esse incidente vai se encerrar amanhã...{WF/Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.08,0:25:25.13,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{and the outcome will shock\Nthe world in an unexpected way. - OG}e seu desfecho vai chocar\No mundo como nada antes.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.34,0:25:30.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.43,0:25:33.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is this all your doing?! - OG}Isso tudo foi você?!{Camo/WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.18,0:25:34.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Responde!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.67,0:26:09.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wh-Why did you do this? - OG}Por que você fez isso...{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.09,0:26:13.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,York?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.02,0:26:20.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Stella! - OG}Adivinha, Stella!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.89,0:26:23.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm going to become a Celestial Dragon! - OG}Eu vou me tornar um Dragão Celestial!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.94,0:26:28.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Do que você tá falando, York?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.19,0:26:30.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você já foi a Mary Geoise, não foi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.69,0:26:33.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you want to be as filthy as they are?! - OG}Você realmente quer ser\Numa daquelas pessoas vis?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.95,0:26:36.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é coisa que o Shaka diria.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.53,0:26:40.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas ele tá morto agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.33,0:26:44.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's confusing. - OG}É complicado demais.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.12,0:26:45.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Somos todos Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.46,0:26:50.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wouldn't one Dr. Vegapunk be... - OG}O mundo precisa mesmo...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.51,0:26:54.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{enough in this world? - OG}de mais de um Vegapunk?{WF}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=73}===============================DIALOGUE============================
